MEMBERSHIP CATEGORIES
RESIDENT MEMBERSHIP
Resident members of the Club shall be confined to persons who are at least twenty-one (21) years of age and who are residents of Hillsborough County, Florida.
INTERMEDIATE MEMBERSHIP
Intermediate members of the Club shall be confined to persons who possess the qualifications of Resident members but who have not attained the age of thirty-five (35) years.
CORPORATE MEMBERSHIP
Each Corporation shall be granted four Corporate Memberships. All four Corporate members shall be sponsored by the Corporation upon Board approval shall become Corporate members. A Corporate member may be replaced by another Corporate sponsored member, however at no time shall there be less than four active Corporate members for each Corporation.
NON-RESIDENT MEMBERSHIP
Non-Resident members of the Club shall be defined as persons who neither reside nor have their principal places of business in Hillsborough County, Florida.
LEGACY MEMBERSHIP
Legacy Members shall be at least twenty-one (21) years of age and shall be confined to linear descendants of a UClub member.
